/* text-align by default is :left
text-align\
vertical-align->top
 text-decoration-line: underline;
 text-decoration-line: overline
 text-decoration-line: line-through;

text-decoration-line: underline overline line-through;
underline -> under the line
overline -> top of the line
line-through -> cut the line
you can color to the line and type of line you want with the style
text-decoration-color: green ;
text-decoration-style: dashed;
text-decoration-thickness-> the thickness of the line
text-decoration-thickness: 10px;

write all of them in the single line
"text-decoration-line: underline overline line-through;
text-decoration-color: green ;
text-decoration-style: dotted;
text-decoration-thickness: 10px;"

 as the text-decoration: overline purple solid 60px;
text-decoration: none; -> deals everthing as none. even the other with the default colors

text-transform: lowercase-> make everthing in lowercase
text-transform: uppercase-> make everything in uppercase
text-transform: capitalize> make everything in start with the capital letter.
text-indent: 30px; indent your text with the space in front.
letter-spacing: 30px;-> give space to letters in the each word. effects evrthing
example : H i
          T o m i
font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; -> font style
font-style:italic;
font-style: oblique;
font-style: normal;-> same way as normal;
font-weight: bold; -> 
font size: 50em -> 50px = 1em.


;*/

